        "Heading_size": "h2",
        "Heading_color": "#aac4d3",
        "title": "ON THE VINES",
        "video-sec-content-txt-1": "<p>With an ideal Mediterranean microclimate, an abundance of soil diversity and water from the life-giving Breede River, the Alvi’s Drift vineyards are ideally positioned for producing remarkable South African wines of unique character and complexity.</p><p>Our Reserve range showcases the best of our harvest; a fusion of our trademark fresh, primary-fruit style – with just a hint of the luscious and opulent barrel-fermented style of our Albertus Viljoen Icon range.</p>",
        "button-txt": "",
        "button_link": "",
        "button_type": "alvisBtn"
